1
00:01:30,920 --> 00:01:32,760
(Episode 33)

2
00:01:38,160 --> 00:01:39,080
Xiaomeng.

3
00:01:39,480 --> 00:01:40,280
Mom.

4
00:01:40,360 --> 00:01:41,400
Where have you been?

5
00:01:41,800 --> 00:01:43,360
I was at work.

6
00:01:45,840 --> 00:01:46,920
Are you tired?

7
00:01:48,520 --> 00:01:52,000
I'm fine. I'm not tired.

8
00:01:54,920 --> 00:01:56,000
What's the matter?

9
00:01:56,800 --> 00:01:58,160
Did someone do you wrong?

10
00:01:58,880 --> 00:01:59,720
No.

11
00:02:01,160 --> 00:02:04,280
The children's play
that we have been rehearsing for

12
00:02:04,360 --> 00:02:05,440
has been suspended.

13
00:02:06,120 --> 00:02:07,160
Why?

14
00:02:08,160 --> 00:02:10,080
The investment was withdrawn...

15
00:02:10,360 --> 00:02:11,600
because the investors are not optimistic

16
00:02:11,680 --> 00:02:12,920
about the prospect of children's plays.

17
00:02:14,080 --> 00:02:16,560
Forget it. You won't understand

18
00:02:16,640 --> 00:02:17,880
what I'm talking about.

19
00:02:18,920 --> 00:02:21,840
Xiaomeng, don't be afraid.

20
00:02:22,120 --> 00:02:24,240
You are a tough girl.

21
00:02:24,600 --> 00:02:26,360
You can do anything.

22
00:02:27,640 --> 00:02:29,320
Have you forgotten
when you were a child,...

23
00:02:30,480 --> 00:02:31,800
you had such a hard time

24
00:02:31,880 --> 00:02:33,120
in primary school.

25
00:02:33,200 --> 00:02:34,920
Didn't you make it through?

26
00:02:35,400 --> 00:02:36,280
It'll be fine.

27
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:40,800
It just never

28
00:02:40,880 --> 00:02:42,080
occurred to me that...

29
00:02:42,680 --> 00:02:43,960
money

30
00:02:44,040 --> 00:02:45,480
is so important.

31
00:02:46,400 --> 00:02:47,640
But I won't give up.

32
00:02:48,120 --> 00:02:49,080
I will fight

33
00:02:49,160 --> 00:02:50,600
for the career that I like.

34
00:02:51,200 --> 00:02:52,120
I will work hard.

35
00:02:54,240 --> 00:02:56,520
Moreover, A Yan is here.

36
00:02:57,320 --> 00:02:58,840
He will help you.

37
00:03:00,600 --> 00:03:03,120
Mom, I can't always

38
00:03:03,320 --> 00:03:05,520
rely on A Yan's help.

39
00:03:06,560 --> 00:03:07,480
When my work

40
00:03:07,560 --> 00:03:08,520
has become stable,...

41
00:03:08,800 --> 00:03:10,120
everything will be fine.

42
00:03:10,320 --> 00:03:11,200
Then I will...

43
00:03:11,600 --> 00:03:13,560
take you on a trip. How does it sound?

44
00:03:17,520 --> 00:03:19,040
So, mom,...

45
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:21,560
you have to get well soon.

46
00:04:06,640 --> 00:04:07,440
Hello.

47
00:04:07,520 --> 00:04:08,320
A Yan, it's me.

48
00:04:09,400 --> 00:04:10,520
Let's meet up and talk.

49
00:04:11,960 --> 00:04:13,680
Sure, let's meet at our usual spot.

50
00:04:24,920 --> 00:04:25,800
Qiao Zhen.

51
00:04:25,960 --> 00:04:26,760
Xiaomeng,

52
00:04:26,880 --> 00:04:28,080
I was very busy.

53
00:04:28,160 --> 00:04:29,480
I'm coming over now. Wait for me.

54
00:04:29,560 --> 00:04:30,360
There's no need.

55
00:04:30,480 --> 00:04:31,840
I know you are busy.

56
00:04:32,360 --> 00:04:33,720
I raised funds for a while

57
00:04:33,800 --> 00:04:35,000
and I'm home now.

58
00:04:36,360 --> 00:04:38,280
You distributed fliers and raised funds?

59
00:04:38,520 --> 00:04:40,520
Yes, but I didn't

60
00:04:40,600 --> 00:04:41,560
print out a lot,...

61
00:04:41,840 --> 00:04:43,200
so they are almost gone.

62
00:04:43,680 --> 00:04:44,480
Fantastic.

63
00:04:44,680 --> 00:04:46,320
How much did you raise today?

64
00:04:47,800 --> 00:04:48,920
Like you said,

65
00:04:49,040 --> 00:04:50,680
people are used to fundraising.

66
00:04:51,320 --> 00:04:52,880
I got around 700 yuan in total

67
00:04:53,040 --> 00:04:54,640
and I have around 4,000 yuan here.

68
00:04:54,880 --> 00:04:56,280
I plan to make it to 5,000 yuan
tomorrow

69
00:04:56,360 --> 00:04:57,600
and transfer it to the director.

70
00:04:59,000 --> 00:05:01,360
Xiaomeng, you are so kind.

71
00:05:02,760 --> 00:05:05,160
I've just got paid.

72
00:05:05,360 --> 00:05:06,280
I will transfer the money to you later.

73
00:05:06,400 --> 00:05:07,600
It's alright, Qiao Zhen.

74
00:05:09,080 --> 00:05:09,880
I know that

75
00:05:09,960 --> 00:05:11,440
you also need money...

76
00:05:11,720 --> 00:05:12,800
and it's not easy

77
00:05:12,880 --> 00:05:13,760
for Dr. Xiao to earn money.

78
00:05:13,880 --> 00:05:14,880
Don't transfer the money to me.

79
00:05:15,360 --> 00:05:16,160
I'm telling you,

80
00:05:16,240 --> 00:05:17,240
cut the nonsense.

81
00:05:17,400 --> 00:05:18,600
Although I don't have much money,

82
00:05:18,680 --> 00:05:20,120
I have to do something.

83
00:05:21,520 --> 00:05:22,440
Round up the sum

84
00:05:22,520 --> 00:05:23,640
with my money.

85
00:05:24,040 --> 00:05:24,960
Just don't mind it's not much.

86
00:05:25,200 --> 00:05:26,280
I'll make the transfer now.

87
00:05:27,240 --> 00:05:28,040
Wait for me.

88
00:05:51,880 --> 00:05:54,040
What are you doing now?
Have you left the office?

89
00:05:56,840 --> 00:05:58,280
What a coincidence!

90
00:05:58,480 --> 00:05:59,480
I just thought of you

91
00:05:59,560 --> 00:06:00,560
and you sent me a message.

92
00:06:01,840 --> 00:06:02,800
I'm so happy.

93
00:06:03,680 --> 00:06:04,480
Didn't you say you want to

94
00:06:04,560 --> 00:06:05,400
have Japanese food?

95
00:06:05,760 --> 00:06:06,640
Let's go tonight.

96
00:06:10,680 --> 00:06:11,520
Forget it.

97
00:06:11,800 --> 00:06:13,160
Japanese food is too expensive.

98
00:06:13,880 --> 00:06:15,200
Let's have Malatang tonight.

99
00:06:25,600 --> 00:06:26,400
How's the progress

100
00:06:26,480 --> 00:06:27,320
of your financing?

101
00:06:28,280 --> 00:06:29,120
It's still in the process of negotiation.

102
00:06:31,440 --> 00:06:33,280
I understand. It's not easy.

103
00:06:39,240 --> 00:06:40,600
Since I took over Shenghai,...

104
00:06:41,600 --> 00:06:43,400
there have been challenges
again and again.

105
00:06:44,160 --> 00:06:46,520
None of it is easy to deal with.

106
00:06:47,400 --> 00:06:49,000
The bigger the goal,...

107
00:06:49,440 --> 00:06:50,480
the more the challenges.

108
00:06:52,560 --> 00:06:54,440
My dad spent a lifetime to build Shenghai.

109
00:06:55,200 --> 00:06:56,000
I will make sure

110
00:06:56,080 --> 00:06:57,040
it does well.

111
00:06:57,360 --> 00:06:58,360
The shrinking of capital...

112
00:06:58,880 --> 00:07:00,800
leading to the suspension of projects
and the collapse of the company,...

113
00:07:01,720 --> 00:07:03,720
I won't let it end up that way.

114
00:07:07,720 --> 00:07:10,360
I know the Dikai Commercial City
incident...

115
00:07:10,640 --> 00:07:12,240
has affected Shenghai badly.

116
00:07:12,880 --> 00:07:13,760
I'm sorry.

117
00:07:16,080 --> 00:07:17,200
It's no use...

118
00:07:17,960 --> 00:07:19,160
talking about what had happened.

119
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:22,040
How about you? What's the matter today?

120
00:07:24,200 --> 00:07:25,960
I just think in many occasions

121
00:07:26,200 --> 00:07:28,400
we aren't free to do what we want.

122
00:07:29,360 --> 00:07:31,160
We can't follow our hearts
to do what we like.

123
00:07:32,280 --> 00:07:34,360
It's like a ship without a helm,...

124
00:07:34,680 --> 00:07:36,200
following the flow of wind and waves.

125
00:07:36,680 --> 00:07:38,040
We don't have a say at all.

126
00:07:39,160 --> 00:07:41,640
Same here. We are in the same boat.

127
00:07:49,520 --> 00:07:51,800
You know that I want to help you...

128
00:07:52,480 --> 00:07:53,760
but there's not much I can do.

129
00:07:55,040 --> 00:07:56,000
Also,...

130
00:07:56,880 --> 00:07:58,120
I am a Jiang after all.

131
00:08:03,400 --> 00:08:04,200
I'm happy enough

132
00:08:04,280 --> 00:08:05,400
that you think this way.

133
00:08:11,040 --> 00:08:12,000
Have you seen this guy?

134
00:08:16,000 --> 00:08:18,080
No, who is he?

135
00:08:21,160 --> 00:08:22,480
Someone who is...

136
00:08:23,320 --> 00:08:24,720
related to the Zhou family.

137
00:08:59,320 --> 00:09:00,200
It's delicious.

138
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:04,760
Mom, wait a minute.

139
00:09:07,280 --> 00:09:08,280
Hello.

140
00:09:08,680 --> 00:09:10,080
This is Zheng, Art Director of

141
00:09:10,160 --> 00:09:11,880
Golden Bridge Culture Company.

142
00:09:13,960 --> 00:09:15,440
Qiao Zhen sent me

143
00:09:15,520 --> 00:09:16,400
your performance proposal.

144
00:09:17,960 --> 00:09:19,920
Hello, Director Zheng.

145
00:09:20,320 --> 00:09:21,560
I am very interested

146
00:09:21,720 --> 00:09:22,840
in your performance proposal.

147
00:09:23,040 --> 00:09:24,960
Let's find time to talk about it.

148
00:09:25,040 --> 00:09:25,840
How does that sound?

149
00:09:25,920 --> 00:09:26,720
Sure.

150
00:09:26,800 --> 00:09:28,640
-When will you have time?
-Why not...

151
00:09:28,920 --> 00:09:30,360
you come to my place now

152
00:09:30,440 --> 00:09:31,320
to discuss about it?

153
00:09:31,760 --> 00:09:35,080
Your place... well...

154
00:09:36,560 --> 00:09:38,160
Don't get it wrong.

155
00:09:38,680 --> 00:09:40,640
Today is my daughter's birthday.

156
00:09:41,040 --> 00:09:42,960
She likes
your Fairy Tale Street very much.

157
00:09:43,960 --> 00:09:45,240
I hope you can

158
00:09:45,320 --> 00:09:46,480
come here and perform

159
00:09:46,560 --> 00:09:47,600
at her birthday party.

160
00:09:47,840 --> 00:09:49,040
If my daughter is happy,

161
00:09:49,280 --> 00:09:51,480
it's easier for me to decide
on the investment.

162
00:09:52,760 --> 00:09:53,560
Alright.

163
00:09:53,880 --> 00:09:55,520
Please send me

164
00:09:55,600 --> 00:09:56,400
your address.

165
00:09:56,480 --> 00:09:57,800
Good. See you later.

166
00:10:01,080 --> 00:10:01,880
Xiaoyu.

167
00:10:05,400 --> 00:10:06,560
What is it, Sister Xiaomeng?

168
00:10:07,040 --> 00:10:08,560
I need to go out for business later.

169
00:10:08,720 --> 00:10:09,960
Please take care of my mom.

170
00:10:10,160 --> 00:10:11,880
Sure, Sister Xiaomeng. Get going.

171
00:10:11,960 --> 00:10:13,200
Don't worry. I am here at home.

172
00:10:20,120 --> 00:10:21,120
Let me feed you, Aunt Ye.

173
00:11:08,040 --> 00:11:08,840
Xiaomeng.

174
00:11:09,440 --> 00:11:10,640
Jiang Ze.

175
00:11:10,840 --> 00:11:11,760
What are you doing here?

176
00:11:13,080 --> 00:11:15,440
I am here for business.

177
00:11:15,880 --> 00:11:16,800
What is it about?

178
00:11:18,720 --> 00:11:20,200
What's in your bag?

179
00:11:23,200 --> 00:11:24,680
Isn't that your costume?

180
00:11:24,800 --> 00:11:25,880
Why have you brought it out with you?

181
00:11:26,720 --> 00:11:27,600
Give it back to me.

182
00:11:27,680 --> 00:11:29,120
I won't give you back
if you don't tell me.

183
00:11:30,840 --> 00:11:31,720
Someone is investing

184
00:11:31,800 --> 00:11:32,840
in our children's play.

185
00:11:33,200 --> 00:11:34,320
It's the birthday

186
00:11:34,400 --> 00:11:35,400
of the investor's daughter.

187
00:11:35,800 --> 00:11:36,640
He asked me to

188
00:11:36,720 --> 00:11:38,000
come to his daughter's birthday party...

189
00:11:38,960 --> 00:11:40,320
to perform.

190
00:11:40,720 --> 00:11:42,000
What? How dare he asked you

191
00:11:42,080 --> 00:11:43,200
to perform for a little girl!

192
00:11:43,280 --> 00:11:44,080
What's his name? Where is he?

193
00:11:44,160 --> 00:11:45,720
-I'm going to see him.
-Alright.

194
00:11:46,240 --> 00:11:47,680
I have promised him...

195
00:11:48,280 --> 00:11:49,400
and I need to

196
00:11:49,480 --> 00:11:50,560
talk to him about the investment.

197
00:11:50,760 --> 00:11:51,880
Can you not interfere in this?

198
00:11:52,000 --> 00:11:52,800
I can't.

199
00:11:52,880 --> 00:11:54,280
He is obviously taking advantage of you.

200
00:11:55,360 --> 00:11:57,400
I have given him my word.

201
00:11:57,800 --> 00:11:59,360
It's not good to go back on my word.

202
00:12:00,760 --> 00:12:01,680
I'll go with you then.

203
00:12:02,280 --> 00:12:03,120
Forget it.

204
00:12:03,520 --> 00:12:05,280
You are living in the same neighborhood.

205
00:12:05,440 --> 00:12:06,960
It'll be awkward for you to meet
each other.

206
00:12:07,400 --> 00:12:09,440
I beg you to leave it alone.

207
00:12:10,120 --> 00:12:11,840
At least let me see you to the door.

208
00:12:14,840 --> 00:12:15,760
Alright.

209
00:12:27,560 --> 00:12:29,160
Alright. This is the place.

210
00:12:29,800 --> 00:12:31,240
You really don't need me
to go in with you?

211
00:12:31,480 --> 00:12:32,640
There's really no need.

212
00:12:32,840 --> 00:12:34,040
I can go in myself.

213
00:12:44,640 --> 00:12:46,280
Hello, I am the performer

214
00:12:46,360 --> 00:12:47,280
for the birthday party.

215
00:12:47,520 --> 00:12:48,320
Come in then.

216
00:13:06,040 --> 00:13:07,360
Zheng Hua?

217
00:13:11,840 --> 00:13:12,640
Hello.

218
00:13:19,560 --> 00:13:20,360
Are you Zhou Xiaomeng

219
00:13:20,440 --> 00:13:21,280
of Fairy Tale Street?

220
00:13:22,400 --> 00:13:23,200
Yes.

221
00:13:23,280 --> 00:13:24,200
Don't seduce Director Zheng

222
00:13:24,280 --> 00:13:25,400
with your young and pretty face.

223
00:13:26,040 --> 00:13:26,840
-No, I won't.
-Alright.

224
00:13:26,920 --> 00:13:27,920
Take these out.

225
00:13:29,200 --> 00:13:30,080
Xiaomeng.

226
00:13:31,000 --> 00:13:31,800
Director Zheng.

227
00:13:32,280 --> 00:13:33,080
Who told you to

228
00:13:33,160 --> 00:13:33,960
ask Xiaomeng to take these things?

229
00:13:34,400 --> 00:13:35,840
She is invited to perform.

230
00:13:36,080 --> 00:13:36,920
Take these out by yourself.

231
00:13:37,480 --> 00:13:38,360
It's fine, Director Zheng.

232
00:13:38,440 --> 00:13:39,240
I'll do it.

233
00:13:40,000 --> 00:13:41,600
Come on, give it to me.

234
00:13:43,080 --> 00:13:44,200
It's alright, Director Zheng.

235
00:13:44,520 --> 00:13:45,840
I will take this in.

236
00:13:50,640 --> 00:13:52,280
What are you looking at? Get back to work.

237
00:14:04,080 --> 00:14:04,880
Hello.

238
00:14:05,240 --> 00:14:06,400
You'd better come back now.

239
00:14:06,760 --> 00:14:07,920
Come on, let's have some cake.

240
00:14:08,000 --> 00:14:08,800
Lulu,

241
00:14:08,920 --> 00:14:09,800
are you happy today?

242
00:14:10,560 --> 00:14:12,000
Let's sing a birthday song

243
00:14:12,200 --> 00:14:13,800
for Lulu.

244
00:14:13,880 --> 00:14:15,520
Sure.

245
00:14:15,760 --> 00:14:19,400
♪Happy birthday to you♪

246
00:14:19,600 --> 00:14:23,560
♪Happy birthday to you♪

247
00:14:23,760 --> 00:14:27,440
♪Happy birthday to you♪

248
00:14:27,520 --> 00:14:31,840
♪Happy birthday to you♪

249
00:14:33,040 --> 00:14:34,240
Lulu, Dad has arranged

250
00:14:34,320 --> 00:14:35,360
a performance for you.

251
00:14:35,520 --> 00:14:37,600
It's Snow White. Do you like it?

252
00:14:37,720 --> 00:14:39,960
Yes.

253
00:14:46,480 --> 00:14:49,600
A long time ago,

254
00:14:49,760 --> 00:14:52,480
Snow White lived in a kingdom.

255
00:14:52,720 --> 00:14:56,200
She was innocent and pretty,
kind and sweet.

256
00:14:56,800 --> 00:14:58,040
She led a carefree life

257
00:14:58,240 --> 00:15:01,120
in the kingdom.

258
00:15:02,200 --> 00:15:03,480
However, one day...

259
00:15:03,880 --> 00:15:05,320
the king of the kingdom...

260
00:15:05,760 --> 00:15:07,080
passed away.

261
00:15:07,800 --> 00:15:09,120
The queen, her stepmother,

262
00:15:09,280 --> 00:15:10,640
took control of everything.

263
00:15:11,320 --> 00:15:12,240
The story...

264
00:15:12,680 --> 00:15:14,560
begins here.

265
00:15:16,400 --> 00:15:18,720
Snow White

266
00:15:18,880 --> 00:15:19,960
met seven dwarves

267
00:15:20,120 --> 00:15:22,080
in a forest.

268
00:15:22,240 --> 00:15:23,080
Hold on.

269
00:15:24,120 --> 00:15:26,160
You don't just play Snow White.

270
00:15:26,240 --> 00:15:27,920
You have to play the seven dwarves
as well.

271
00:15:28,000 --> 00:15:31,040
Yes, you have to play the seven dwarves.

272
00:15:33,560 --> 00:15:36,520
Sure, I will play dwarves

273
00:15:36,600 --> 00:15:37,480
for you.

274
00:15:39,200 --> 00:15:40,720
The dwarves and Snow White

275
00:15:40,800 --> 00:15:43,680
walked in the forest.

276
00:15:43,960 --> 00:15:44,800
Wait a minute.

277
00:15:45,520 --> 00:15:46,960
Dwarves are short.

278
00:15:47,120 --> 00:15:50,280
-Right, dwarves are short!
-Short.

279
00:15:53,360 --> 00:15:54,360
Alright.

280
00:15:54,880 --> 00:15:57,840
Then I will be...

281
00:15:58,760 --> 00:15:59,920
a short dwarf for you.

282
00:16:05,600 --> 00:16:07,640
Dwarves and Snow White

283
00:16:07,720 --> 00:16:10,760
walked in the forest.

284
00:16:10,840 --> 00:16:13,280
The dwarf is so ugly.

285
00:16:13,440 --> 00:16:15,160
Ugly!

286
00:16:15,480 --> 00:16:17,960
-So ugly.
-It's awful.

287
00:16:21,200 --> 00:16:22,680
So ugly.

288
00:16:24,560 --> 00:16:26,200
So ugly.

289
00:16:31,840 --> 00:16:32,880
