00:38:49,720 --> 00:38:50,720
I'll get you something to eat

868
00:38:50,800 --> 00:38:51,760
right away.

869
00:38:56,560 --> 00:38:58,440
This is our children's play.

870
00:38:58,680 --> 00:39:00,040
It was suspended

871
00:39:00,120 --> 00:39:00,960
because of a shortage in capital.

872
00:39:01,240 --> 00:39:02,480
But somehow

873
00:39:02,680 --> 00:39:03,680
the original company

874
00:39:03,760 --> 00:39:05,120
decided to invest again.

875
00:39:05,280 --> 00:39:06,080
Now,

876
00:39:06,160 --> 00:39:07,480
Yang Xi and I will play the major roles.

877
00:39:08,480 --> 00:39:09,360
You will play Peter Pan?

878
00:39:10,240 --> 00:39:11,760
The boy who will never grow up?

879
00:39:13,120 --> 00:39:14,080
The director...

880
00:39:14,240 --> 00:39:15,760
said I fit this character.

881
00:39:16,160 --> 00:39:17,720
I'd also like to be...

882
00:39:18,480 --> 00:39:20,040
a child forever,

883
00:39:20,200 --> 00:39:21,240
and always live in

884
00:39:21,320 --> 00:39:22,560
a children's world.

885
00:39:23,200 --> 00:39:25,640
I think it's a joy.

886
00:39:27,200 --> 00:39:28,120
It's good that you're happy.

887
00:39:30,040 --> 00:39:30,840
A Yan,...

888
00:39:32,400 --> 00:39:34,680
will you and mom...

889
00:39:35,000 --> 00:39:37,280
come and watch my first performance?

890
00:39:38,800 --> 00:39:43,040
Auntie Lin will also be there.

891
00:39:47,040 --> 00:39:48,080
We'll see when the time comes.

892
00:40:18,560 --> 00:40:20,000
Alright. Almost done.

893
00:40:25,440 --> 00:40:26,440
Xiaomeng, come on.

894
00:40:26,560 --> 00:40:27,520
Let's have a selfie.

895
00:40:27,760 --> 00:40:28,600
Sure.

896
00:40:36,480 --> 00:40:38,320
Xiaomeng, are you nervous?

897
00:40:39,120 --> 00:40:39,960
I'm fine.

898
00:40:40,280 --> 00:40:41,720
After all, we have rehearsed many times,

899
00:40:41,800 --> 00:40:42,960
so I'm not very nervous.

900
00:40:43,040 --> 00:40:45,240
That's right. You'd been through a lot

901
00:40:45,400 --> 00:40:46,600
when you were a host.

902
00:40:46,680 --> 00:40:48,280
This is no big deal.

903
00:40:49,200 --> 00:40:51,960
However, it has been a long time

904
00:40:52,040 --> 00:40:53,680
since I was under the spotlight,...

905
00:40:54,280 --> 00:40:55,840
so I'm still a little worried...

906
00:40:56,280 --> 00:40:57,880
if the audience will like me.

907
00:40:58,200 --> 00:40:59,720
Don't worry. It'll be fine.

908
00:41:05,000 --> 00:41:06,160
Xiaomeng, Yang Xi!

909
00:41:07,160 --> 00:41:08,000
Zitong.

910
00:41:08,600 --> 00:41:10,600
-Zitong.
-All the best to your performance!

911
00:41:10,680 --> 00:41:11,520
Thank you.

912
00:41:12,080 --> 00:41:13,920
Xiaomeng, your makeup is fantastic today.

913
00:41:14,040 --> 00:41:15,560
I'm so looking forward
to your performance.

914
00:41:15,640 --> 00:41:16,440
Really?

915
00:41:16,640 --> 00:41:18,680
Thank you, Zitong.

916
00:41:18,840 --> 00:41:20,440
You come to see us
even though you're busy.

917
00:41:20,520 --> 00:41:21,320
Of course.

918
00:41:21,520 --> 00:41:23,120
You are my best friends.

919
00:41:23,200 --> 00:41:24,200
How can I miss

920
00:41:24,280 --> 00:41:25,720
your performance?

921
00:41:26,040 --> 00:41:26,960
Right, Qiao Zhen said

922
00:41:27,040 --> 00:41:27,920
she was held up by work at the station.

923
00:41:28,000 --> 00:41:29,000
She would come later.

924
00:41:29,080 --> 00:41:29,880
Sure.

925
00:41:30,360 --> 00:41:31,240
How is it?

926
00:41:32,200 --> 00:41:33,600
-Does it look good?
-Yes.

927
00:41:33,680 --> 00:41:35,720
Your costume is exactly as it is described
in the book.

928
00:41:36,720 --> 00:41:37,600
Relax.

929
00:41:39,520 --> 00:41:40,560
Don't get nervous later.

930
00:41:41,200 --> 00:41:42,280
There are so many people here.

931
00:41:45,840 --> 00:41:46,760
Jiang Ze.

932
00:41:46,880 --> 00:41:47,920
Jiang Ze.

933
00:41:48,960 --> 00:41:50,680
Why do you have time today?

934
00:41:55,920 --> 00:41:56,800
Good luck, Xiaomeng.

935
00:42:01,400 --> 00:42:02,720
Why isn't A Yan here?

936
00:42:05,040 --> 00:42:05,840
Director Lin

937
00:42:05,920 --> 00:42:07,200
has brought Tiankong and the rest here.

938
00:42:07,560 --> 00:42:09,640
Dr. Xiao and my mom are here too.

939
00:42:10,040 --> 00:42:12,640
A Yan may be

940
00:42:12,720 --> 00:42:14,160
held up by business.

941
00:42:14,800 --> 00:42:16,280
Jiang Ze, have you come

942
00:42:16,360 --> 00:42:17,760
to see Xiaomeng empty-handed?

943
00:42:18,720 --> 00:42:20,160
How could that be?

944
00:42:20,600 --> 00:42:21,600
I have prepared a whole carton

945
00:42:21,680 --> 00:42:22,560
of French champagne.

946
00:42:22,720 --> 00:42:23,880
We will celebrate

947
00:42:23,960 --> 00:42:25,200
-with our superstar later.
-Champagne!

948
00:42:25,280 --> 00:42:27,600
-Great. Fantastic.
-Come here.

949
00:42:27,680 --> 00:42:28,520
Five minutes to go.

950
00:42:28,600 --> 00:42:29,560
The backstage should get ready now.

951
00:42:29,760 --> 00:42:30,720
Okay, director.

952
00:42:31,240 --> 00:42:32,040
Alright.

953
00:42:32,120 --> 00:42:33,120
Let's wait at the auditorium.

954
00:42:33,240 --> 00:42:34,280
Let them calm down for a while.

955
00:42:34,640 --> 00:42:35,800
-Let's go.
-Bye.

956
00:42:36,280 --> 00:42:37,120
Five minutes to go.

957
00:42:37,240 --> 00:42:38,080
-Good luck.
-I will.

958
00:42:38,160 --> 00:42:39,360
-Let's go.
-I can't wait for your show. Good luck.

959
00:42:39,920 --> 00:42:40,880
-Good luck.
-Good luck.

960
00:42:42,240 --> 00:42:43,160
My Peter Pan,

961
00:42:43,240 --> 00:42:44,720
you have to put on a good show!

962
00:42:45,000 --> 00:42:45,920
My Wendy,

963
00:42:46,040 --> 00:42:47,240
you are my best friend.

964
00:42:47,400 --> 00:42:48,800
-We will fight together.
-Fight together!
